<div class="container black singoff">
	<h3>Team Cap</h3>
	<p>Each school may send a maximum of 4 participants from which 2 will be taking part in Eastern singing and 2 in western. All the participants must be accompanied by an instrumental or live music comprised of not more than 2 instruments.</p>
	<h3>Procedure</h3>
	<p>A total of 3 rounds will be observed. Procedure will remain same for both categories.</p>
	<h3>Round 1</h3>
	<p>All the participants must come prepared with one song and the results for this round will be announced an hour after the round ends.</p>
	<h3>Round 2</h3>
	<p>6 participants will enter this round qualifying from round 1. All the singers must choose their songs carefully and smartly as the judges will be testing whether the song chosen is demonstrating their ability or not.</p>
	<h3>Round 3 (Final round)</h3>
	<p>3 participants will enter this round qualifying from the previous round. The procedure is same for this round as was for the previous round.</p>
	<h3>Rules</h3>
	<ul><li>The song duration must not be less than 2 minutes and not more than 5 minutes including sound check and all the necessary things to be done before performance.</li><li>Music is compulsory for all rounds no participant will be allowed to sing without music, it may be a live instrument or a karaoke.</li><li>Mashups or medleys are not allowed all singers must prepare a single song for any round.</li><li>Participant having a Karaoke containing background vocals will be penalized.</li><li>Before starting a performance the participants have to introduce themselves as well as the song to the judges.</li><li>Use of foul language or other profanity in lyrics will result in disqualification.</li></ul>
	<h3>Judging Criteria</h3>
	<ul><li>Voice quality</li><li>Song choice</li><li>Rhythm and tempo</li><li>Clarity of lyrics</li><li>Stage presence and body language</li></ul>
	<h3>Award</h3>
	<ul><li>Winner (Eastern category)</li><li>Winner (Western category)</li><li>Runner up (Eastern category)</li><li>Runner up (Western category)</li></ul>
</div> 